databricks-init-scripts

Overview

A repository of Databricks cluster init scripts.


Install

You can set up a Databricks repo to clone this project to your workspace.


Usage

How to use cluster-scoped init scripts


Code of Conduct

Please note that the databricks-init-scripts project is released with a Contributor Code of Conduct. By contributing to this project, you agree to abide by its terms.


About

Washington University in Saint Louis

Established in 1853, Washington University in Saint Louis is among the worlds leaders in teaching, research, patient care, and service to society. Boasting 24 Nobel laureates to date, the University is ranked 7th in the world for most cited researchers, received the 4th highest amount of NIH medical research grants among medical schools in 2019, and was tied for 1st in the United States for genetics and genomics in 2018. The University is committed to learning and exploration, discovery and impact, and intellectual passions and challenging the unknown.
